OL,3,CAround 800,000 homes in Wales warned
OL,4,Cabout disused coal tips
OL,6,FAround 800,000 homes in Wales have
OL,7,Fbeen signposted to advice about
OL,8,Fdisused coal tips as the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment continues inspecting
OL,10,Fpotentially dangerous sites.
OL,12,FThe new safety and awareness campaign
OL,13,Fcomes after the Disused Mine and
OL,14,FQuarry Tips (Wales) Act passed through
OL,15,Fthe Senedd earlier this year and has
OL,16,Fnow received Royal Assent.
OL,18,FThis new law will establish a body
OL,19,Fresponsible for checking, recording,
OL,20,Fmonitoring and managing tips from 2027.
