OL,3,CAround 800,000 homes in Wales warned
OL,4,Cabout disused coal tips
OL,6,FThe Government says R category tips
OL,7,Fare also very unlikely to impact
OL,8,Fpublic safety and have been
OL,9,Fpotentially removed or levelled and
OL,10,Foften built over.
OL,12,FThe new law comes after two high
OL,13,Fprofile landslips from coal tips in
OL,14,Frecent years.
OL,16,FDozens of people were evacuated from
OL,17,Ftheir homes in Cwmtillery, Blaenau
OL,18,FGwent, in November 2024 following a
OL,19,Flandslip caused by Storm Bert. This
OL,20,Fwas later confirmed to have come from
OL,21,Fa category D site.
