OL,3,CAround 800,000 homes in Wales warned
OL,4,Cabout disused coal tips
OL,6,FNeath Port Talbot has the highest
OL,7,Fnumber of sites at 620, but Rhondda
OL,8,FCynon Taf has the highest number of
OL,9,FCategory D tips (most at risk) at 29
OL,10,Fsites.
OL,12,FThe UK Government recently agreed to
OL,13,Fprovide record funding of #118m over
OL,14,Fthree years for coal tip safety. When
OL,15,Fcombined with the Welsh Government's
OL,16,Finvestment, it means more than #220m
OL,17,Fhas been invested in coal tip safety
OL,18,Fto date.
