OL,3,CAround 800,000 homes in Wales warned
OL,4,Cabout disused coal tips
OL,6,FHowever questions have been raised as
OL,7,Fto whether this is enough to make the
OL,8,Fsites safe when considering the scale
OL,9,Fof the challenge.
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister with
OL,12,Fresponsibility for Climate Change, Huw
OL,13,FIrranca-Davies, said: "The regular
OL,14,Fupdating of this national, publicly
OL,15,Favailable data demonstrates our
OL,16,Funwavering commitment to coal tip
OL,17,Fsafety across Wales, and our absolute
OL,18,Fdedication to protecting people.
