OL,3,CAround 800,000 homes in Wales warned
OL,4,Cabout disused coal tips
OL,6,F"I want to reassure people living near
OL,7,Fto where tips have moved categories
OL,8,Fthat this means they will receive
OL,9,Fincreased monitoring and management as
OL,10,FWales continues to lead the way in
OL,11,Faddressing the challenge of coal tip
OL,12,Fsafety, and ensuring our communities
OL,13,Fare safe for generations to come.
OL,15,F"This record investment is making real
OL,16,Fsafety improvements for communities
OL,17,Facross Wales. Combining Welsh and UK
OL,18,FGovernment funding effectively helps
OL,19,Fus ensure communities are better
OL,20,Fprotected for the future."
